This catalog contains video composition blocks for HyperFrames
(https://hyperframes.heygen.com — Apache 2.0).

PERMITTED USE
You are free to use the blocks in your own video projects, personal or
commercial. You may:
  - Install any block into your HyperFrames project (via `hyperframes add`,
    git clone, or manual copy).
  - Modify a block's CSS, text, variables, or assets to fit your design.
  - Embed the rendered output in any platform (YouTube, Instagram, TikTok,
    LinkedIn, websites, paid courses, client deliverables, etc.).
  - Use the blocks for commercial purposes including client work and
    monetized content.

PROHIBITED USE
You may NOT:
  - Redistribute the blocks as a standalone product, package, asset bundle,
    or catalog (free or paid).
  - Resell individual blocks, modified versions of them, or any derivative
    catalog built primarily from them.
  - Remove the copyright header from block HTML files when distributing or
    sharing source code publicly.
  - Use the "Tareabox" or "Natalie Digital" names, marks, or logos to imply
    endorsement, partnership, or affiliation with your derivative work
    without written permission.
  - Train machine-learning models on the blocks for the purpose of
    generating competing block catalogs.

ATTRIBUTION
Attribution is appreciated but not required. A "Made with Tareabox blocks"
mention in your project README, video description, or credits is welcome.

THIRD-PARTY DEPENDENCIES
The blocks depend on HyperFrames (Apache 2.0), GSAP (via CDN, Standard
"no-charge" license for many uses), the Geist font (SIL Open Font License),
and stream demo assets from the Pexels CDN (Pexels License, attribution
not required). End users are responsible for complying with those licenses
in their own projects.

